data.title: EVGA SuperNOVA 850 G2 850W Full Modular Power Supply Overview
data.description: Unleash the next generation in power with the EVGA 850G2 Power Supply. Supporting 80 PLUS Gold rated efficiency, it provides clean, continuous power to every component. The new ECO Thermal Control Fan System offers Fan RPM modes to provide zero fan noise during low load operations. This provides improved efficiency for longer operation, less power consumption, reduced energy costs and efficient heat dissipation. Backed by 100% Japanese-capacitor design, the EVGA 850G2 is not only the right choice for your system today, it's the next choice for your system tomorrow.

data.title: Ergotech Triple Desk Stand With Telescoping Wings Overview
data.description: Ergotech Monitor Desk Stands are designed with the user in mind. Constructed with steel and aluminum, Ergotech Desk Stands are lightweight AND strong. With the patented Quick Release Pivots, installation and removal of monitors is quick and easy and requires no tools. Once mounted, the Height Adjustable Pivots provide effortless monitor positioning for left/right/up/down movement, as well as both landscape and portrait views. With the addition of telescoping wings, which give an extra 5 inches on each side, Ergotech's Monitor Desk Stands can hold up to 27" monitors! All Ergotech Desk Stands are free-standing and can upgrade to hold up to six monitors with just a few extra parts.

data.title: Samsung 840 EVO mSATA SSD Installation Tutorial
data.description: The Samsung 840 EVO mSATA SSD features the same read/write speeds and features that have garnered rave reviews for the 2.5" version, but in a much smaller form factor for thin and light laptops and ultrabooks (some motherboards too!). If you have an ultrabook or laptop with mSATA, but you feel limited with your existing SSD's space and/or performance, watch this video for a tutorial on the installation process and imaging your current Windows installation to the new drive."

data.title: Tek Republic TUD-3000 USB 3.0 Dual Display Docking Station Overview
data.description: The Tek-Republic Universal USB 3.0 Dual Display Docking Station offers a full range of features including dual video ports (one DVI-I, one HDMI, one VGA) to connect two monitors and three USB 3.0 ports for your USB 3.0 peripherals. The docking station also includes a Gigabit Ethernet port, audio In/Out ports and a security lock slot to help secure the dock. A 4A AC adapter and 3-foot USB 3.0 cable are also included to connect your devices for it to become a complete workstation -- including a mouse, a keyboard, and other peripherals you may need to connect with by simply docking your laptop.

data.title: SILVERSTONE SFX 300W Power Supply Overview
data.description: The Silverstone ST30SF is a newly released 300W SFX power supply with high affordability and great performance. Its semi-fanless design enables silent operation at low loads, and offers aggressive cooling at high loads.

data.title: Creative Sound Blaster Recon3D Omega Wireless Gaming Headset Overview
data.tags: Creative ,Sound, Blaster ,Recon3D, Omega, Wireless ,Gaming, Headset, newegg, neweggtv, newegg tv
data.description: Powered by the revolutionary Sound Core3D quad-core sound and voice processor, the Sound Blaster Recon3D Omega Wireless audio system heralds the beginning of a new era in gaming audio. It packs amazing audio processing power previously available only in internal PC audio card solutions into a stylish and powerful wireless gaming audio system for your Xbox 360, Playstation 3, PC or Mac. Hardware accelerated THX TruStudio Pro technologies greatly enhance ordinary gaming audio leaving standard 5.1 and 7.1 audio systems in the dust. Once you've experienced the power of Sound Core3D hardware accelerated gaming audio, you'll never settle for anything less. Join the legion of 400 million Sound Blaster users and prepare yourself for truly legendary quality gaming audio.

data.title: Thermaltake Core V71 Extreme Full Tower Chassis Overview
data.description: Experience the epitome of chassis designs! Thermaltake introduces a one of a kind concept for more versatility and adaptability to any configuration. The Core V71 full-tower E-ATX case gives PC enthusiasts flexible installation options and keeps the system cool. Users can modify for superior liquid cooling or superb airflow through seamless operation. This new chassis is the ultimate powerhouse suitable for any type of PC enthusiast -- no matter liquid cooling or extreme airflow.

data.title: Cooler Master Nepton 140XL CPU Liquid Water Cooling System Overview
data.description: The Nepton 140XL brings water cooling to the next level. It features a CM exclusive designed pump and a highly effective waterblock for the best water flow. Dual JetFlo 140 fans supply powerful air pressure, while a 140mm aluminum radiator efficiently cools your system with heat dissipation. The Nepton 140XL also includes robust and extra thick FEB tubing to prevent moisture absorption while maintaining sufficient water flow for performance cooling. Cool your CPU with the Nepton 140XL, so you can overclock it and push performance to the max!

data.title: Tt eSPORTS CRONOS 3.5mm/ USB Connector Headset Overview
data.tags: Tt eSPORTS ,CRONOS, 3.5mm, USB, Connector ,Headset, newegg, newegg tv,
data.description: Featuring 40mm Neodymium Magnet drivers and a three-sectioned headband, the CRONOS gaming headset is designed for gaming enthusiasts who require high-quality sound and continuous comfort. What's more, this headset is optimized for both FPS gaming and mobile use. It comes with two removable headphone cables: one for use with PC gaming, and the other for use with mobile phones.

data.title: AAXA P300 WXGA 1280x800 Resolution Pocket Size Projector with LED Overview
data.description: AAXA Technologies is excited to introduce the P300 Pico Projector -- the brightest HD pocket projector in class. The new P300 features a revolutionary new compact optical engine capable of delivering 300 peak lumens at a high-definition (HD) resolution of 1280x800.
